[481.310414, "o", "[Read]\r\n"]
[512.056184, "o", "Perfect! I've successfully fitted the G and 2D peaks of the graphene Raman spectrum and saved the results to `/app/results.json`.\r\n\r\n**Summary of fitted parameters:**\r\n\r\n**G Peak:**\r\n- **x0 (center)**: 1646.10 cm⁻¹\r\n- **gamma (FWHM)**: 42.65 cm⁻¹  \r\n- **amplitude**: 1242.79\r\n- **offset**: 4896.18\r\n\r\n**2D Peak:**\r\n- **x0 (center)**: 2716.41 cm⁻¹\r\n- **gamma (FWHM)**: 1.00 cm⁻¹\r\n- **amplitude**: 164.34\r\n- **offset**: 371.08\r\n\r\nThe fitting was performed using Lorentzian functions with proper bounds and initial guesses based on the actual data. The results file `/app/results.json` contains all the fitted parameters in the exact format you requested.\r\n"]
[512.12126, "o", "\u001b[?2004hroot@5122f048632d:/app# "]
